| Hook        | Purpose                     |
| ----------- | --------------------------- |
| useState    | manage component state      |
| useEffect   | handle side effects         |
| useRef      | persist values / access DOM |
| useMemo     | cache/memoize expensive values and the function doesnt re run   |
| useContext  | share global data           |
| useCallback | cache/memoize functions reference  but the function re runs everytime       |
